<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>I consider myself a better political analyst than the average schmoe, a lot of political speeches are aimed at people dumber than myself, which makes it slightly easier to pick up on the things that are blatantly not being said.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
