Your percentages are interesting in a sense, but I don't think there was ever a point where the U.S. ever said they were taking Saddam out for one reason and one reason only. It was pretty much always a Chinese menu of reasons for regime change (the actual degree of justification those reasons implied notwithstanding).<br>
