<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>They have missile technology which can hit some of the most highly populated cities in the world, and at a pinch, may well be able to hit mainland USA with a missile. The warheads they may be able to carry would probably be low yeild 20KT type of affairs, but enough to bring death and destruction of an unprecedented level to the US.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
