<br>
Next up, you are suggesting that 20 million people will do something fundamentally different from human nature.<br>
<br>
If you take any random person on the entire planet, and get them angry enough, or beleive in something enough, there will come a point where they will do something, and will not fear the consequences.<br>
<br>
That is a simple, undeniable fact. Human nature.<br>
<br>
<br>
